name: RTCInboundRtpStreamStats.packetsFailedDecryption
description: The packetsFailedDecryption property of the RTCInboundRtpStreamStats dictionary indicates the total number of RTP packets which failed to be decrypted successfully after being received by the local end of the connection during this session.
